    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Importance of Prenatal Influences</strong>&mdash;The effect of prenatal influences is by many parents looked upon as a matter of little moment; but heaven does not so regard it. The message sent by an angel of God, and twice given in the most solemn manner, shows it to be deserving of our most careful thought.",
