    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "But if the mother unswervingly adheres to right principles, if she is temperate and self-denying, if she is kind, gentle, and unselfish, she may give her child these same precious traits of character.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">4<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"MH 372.4\" data-link=\"135.1874\">Ibid., 372, 373</span>.</span></a></sup>",
