    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Maintain a Peaceful, Trustful Attitude</strong>&mdash;She who expects to become a mother should keep her soul in the love of God. Her mind should be at peace; she should rest in the love of Jesus, practicing the words of Christ. She should remember that the mother is a laborer together with God.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">11<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"ST 4-9-1896\" data-link=\"820.13396\">The Signs of the Times, April 9, 1896</span>.</span></a></sup>",
